00:44:54,280 --> 00:44:55,630
(Liquor)
I didn’t expect

863
00:44:55,630 --> 00:44:56,950
(Liquor)
your ambition was limited only to

864
00:44:56,950 --> 00:44:58,950
(Liquor)
escaping skills.

865
00:45:01,600 --> 00:45:02,550
It is of course an ambition.

866
00:45:04,280 --> 00:45:05,320
Look.

867
00:45:05,320 --> 00:45:07,000
I can escape
the Fortress of the Forty-Eight

868
00:45:07,000 --> 00:45:08,430
and the dungeon smoothly.

869
00:45:08,430 --> 00:45:09,460
It is a big ambition already.

870
00:45:25,710 --> 00:45:26,380
But Fei,

871
00:45:27,320 --> 00:45:27,960
I wonder

872
00:45:28,520 --> 00:45:29,630
if your mother will kick me out again

