874
00:45:31,470 --> 00:45:33,050
with you this time.

875
00:45:34,840 --> 00:45:35,870
I don’t think so.

876
00:45:36,840 --> 00:45:38,960
I don’t have another father
for you to take away.

877
00:45:47,040 --> 00:45:48,160
I am just afraid

878
00:45:48,910 --> 00:45:51,020
she may worry about
what is even more valuable to her.

879
00:46:00,760 --> 00:46:04,270
♪Stars flow like river♪

880
00:46:05,330 --> 00:46:08,930
♪My yearning falls into the river♪

881
00:46:09,500 --> 00:46:13,570
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

882
00:46:13,820 --> 00:46:17,460
♪I will never be alone♪

883
00:46:17,460 --> 00:46:21,580
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

884
00:46:22,000 --> 00:46:26,430
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

885
00:46:27,090 --> 00:46:31,650
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

886
00:46:31,880 --> 00:46:36,510
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

887
00:46:36,700 --> 00:46:40,530
♪I fear not to roam the world with you♪

888
00:46:40,750 --> 00:46:45,440
♪When I go across the world for you♪

889
00:46:45,700 --> 00:46:49,440
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

890
00:46:49,770 --> 00:46:54,860
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

891
00:46:54,860 --> 00:46:58,800
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

892
00:46:58,800 --> 00:47:03,330
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

893
00:47:03,950 --> 00:47:11,050
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

894
00:47:11,790 --> 00:47:16,420
♪The purest love is unadorned♪
